        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Tools and Hardware</h2>
          <p>Need a soldering iron, a multimeter or a screwdriver? MsNet has a wide range of tools and hardware that you
            can borrow for your projects.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Machines and Resources</h2>
